<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no" />
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
		<META HTTP-EQUIV="Pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
		<META HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache">
		<META HTTP-EQUIV="Expires" CONTENT="0">
		<title><%= pageTitle %></title>
		<style>
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				font-size: .16rem;
			}
			
			#content {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				width: 90%;
				position: absolute;
				top: .2rem;
				left: 50%;
				overflow: hidden;
				padding-bottom: .3rem;
			}
			
			#content p {
				background: transparent !important;
			}
			
			.title {
				font-size: .30rem;
			}
			
			.avator {
				width: 100%;
			}
			
			.author-wrap {
				margin: .15rem 0;
			}
			
			.author {
				font-size: .16rem;
				color: cornflowerblue;
			}
			
			.date {
				color: #7E7E7E;
				margin-left: .1rem;
			}
			
			.tips {
				float: right;
				width: 100px;
				margin-top: .1rem;
			}
			
			.btn {
				width: 87%;
				white-space: normal;
				border-top: none;
				border-right: none;
				border-bottom: none;
				border-image: initial;
				margin: 30px auto 0;
				padding: 9px;
				font-size: 20px;
				line-height: 25px;
				font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;
				text-shadow: #225F87 0px 1px 0px;
				color: #FFFFFF;
				border-radius: 4px;
				box-shadow: #999999 2px 2px 4px;
				background-color: #e64e5a;
				text-align: center;
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			
			.mask {
				padding-right: 1.5em;
				padding-bottom: 1em;
				line-height: 2;
				padding: 1em 0.5em;
				text-align: left;
				font-size: 18px;
				-webkit-filter: blur(3px);
				filter: blur(3px);
				color: #525252;
				text-indent: 1.5em;
			}
			
			.more {
				text-indent: 2em;
				font-size: 20px;
			}
			
			.more span{
				font-size: 20px;
				color: #e64e5a;
			}
			.chapter-titlt {
				font-size: 18px;
				padding: 30px 0;
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="content">
			<h2 class="title"><%= articleTit %></h2>
			<div class="author-wrap">
				<span class="author"><%= name %></span>
				<span class="date"><%= desc %></span></div>
			<p style="text-align: center;">
				<img class="avator" src="<%= picurl %>">
			</p>
			<div class="chapter-titlt">
					<section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: currentcolor;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
						<section style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
							<section style="box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" class="">
								<section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" class="">
									<section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;width: 5px;height: 2px;border-radius: 3px 3px 0px 0px;float: left;background-color: rgb(218, 203, 158);word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
									<section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;width: 5px;height: 2px;border-radius: 3px 3px 0px 0px;float: right;background-color: rgb(218, 203, 158);word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
									<section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;clear: both;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
								</section>
								<section style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 2px 10px;max-width: 100%;border-left: 5px solid rgb(218, 203, 158);border-right: 5px solid rgb(218, 203, 158);border-top-color: rgb(218, 203, 158);border-bottom-color: rgb(218, 203, 158);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
									<section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="padding:5px 0;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">第 一 章</section>
								</section>
								<section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">
									<section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;width: 5px;height: 2px;border-radius: 0px 0px 3px 3px;float: left;background-color: rgb(218, 203, 158);word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
									<section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;width: 5px;height: 2px;border-radius: 0px 0px 3px 3px;float: right;background-color: rgb(218, 203, 158);word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
									<section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;clear: both;word-wrap: break-word !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
								</section>
							</section>
						</section>
					</section>
				</div>
			<%- capter1 %>	
			<p class="mask">
				“刘洋，餐厅布置好了吗？你再去看一遍，不准出现一丁点儿的纰漏，不然的话我扣你工资……”
			</p>
			<p class="more">更多 <span> 精彩内容 </span> 请点击下一章</p>
			<p>
				<img class="tips" src="/img/tuiguang/icon.png" />
			</p>
			<a href="javascript:;" class="btn">下一章</a>
		</div>
		<%- tokenCodes %>
		<script>
			(function(){
				setTimeout(function(a) {
					if (!document.body) {
					console.log('-------!body')
					 return setTimeout(arguments.callee, 50)
					}
				},50)
				console.log('-------end body')
				function refresh() {
					var width = document.documentElement.clientWidth;
					if(width < 375) {
						document.documentElement.style.fontSize = width / 3.75 + "px";
					} else {
						document.documentElement.style.fontSize = "100px";
					}
				}
				refresh();
				window.onresize = refresh;
				var u = navigator.userAgent;
				var isAndroid = u.indexOf('Android') > -1 || u.indexOf('Adr') > -1; //android终端
				var isiOS = !!u.match(/\(i[^;]+;( U;)? CPU.+Mac OS X/); //ios终端
				if(isAndroid) {
					document.getElementById('content').style.marginLeft = '-45%'
				} else if(isiOS) {
					document.getElementById('content').style.marginLeft = '-43%'
				}
				var btn = document.getElementsByClassName('btn')[0];
				btn.onclick=function(){
					window.location.href = '/tuiguang/capter/<%= id %>'
				}
			})()
		</script>
		<div style="display: none;" data-author="mingxingshuo">
			<%- statisticsUrl1 %>
		</div>
	</body>

</html>